paragraphs.title: FPS Inbound Payment
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)
select "settelment_date" as "Date Settlmnt", "cycle_id" as "Cycle Id","debtor_stortcode" as "Debtor Sort Code","debtor_account" as "Debtor Account Number","creditor_sortcode" as "Creditor sort Code","creditor_account" as "Creditor Account Number","amount" as "Amount","currency" as "Currency","fpid" as "FPID","returned_fpid" as "Interaccount Transfer Id	Related FPID for Return Payments", "payment_id" as "Internal ipagoo Unique Id","customer_reference" as "Customer Reference","status" as "Status of Payment","credit_debit_ind" as "Payment C / D", "direction" as "Direction" from FPS_REPORT_PAYMENTS WHERE "direction"='I' AND "exception_ind" = false  ${searchFPSPaymentReportQuery} order by "creditor_sortcode","settelment_date","cycle_id", "debtor_stortcode"

paragraphs.title: FPS Exceptions
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(phoenix)
select "settelment_date" as "Date Settlmnt", "cycle_id" as "Cycle Id","debtor_stortcode" as "Debtor Sort Code","debtor_account" as "Debtor Account Number","creditor_sortcode" as "Creditor sort Code","creditor_account" as "Creditor Account Number","amount" as "Amount","currency" as "Currency","fpid" as "FPID","returned_fpid" as "Interaccount Transfer Id	Related FPID for Return Payments", "payment_id" as "Internal ipagoo Unique Id","customer_reference" as "Customer Reference","status" as "Status of Payment","failure_reason" as "Failure Reason", "credit_debit_ind" as "Payment C / D", "direction" as "Direction" from FPS_REPORT_PAYMENTS WHERE  "exception_ind" = true  ${searchFPSPaymentReportQuery} order by "creditor_sortcode","settelment_date","cycle_id", "debtor_stortcode"
